<script>
import TopNavbar from "./TopNavbar.vue";
import ContentFooter from "./ContentFooter.vue";
import DashboardContent from "./ContentGen.vue";
import MobileMenu from "./MobileMenu.vue";
export default {
  components: {
    TopNavbar,
    ContentFooter,
    DashboardContent,
    MobileMenu,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      showSidebar: false,
    };
  },
  methods: {
    toggleSidebar() {
      this.showSidebar = !this.showSidebar;
    },
  },
};
</script>
